Package: rnirs
Type: Package
Title: Chemometrics Methods and Locally Weighted PLS Regressions
Version: 1.6-0
Author: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Maintainer: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Description: Package rnirs focuses on chemometrics methods, including locally weighted PLS regressions and discriminations. The package was initially implemented for near infrared spectral (NIRS) data, but is generic for any type of data.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:  data.table, FNN, ggplot2, gridExtra, ptw, scales, signal 
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/mlesnoff/rnirs
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: yes
